{
  "info": {
    "name": "Pawffy — Unified Booking Flow",
    "description": "User-side unified booking flow for Pawffy. Every service type (vet, grooming, walking, training, boarding, sitting, transport, poop_scooper) is a PartnerService on a PartnerBusiness, booked as a single PartnerBooking. Flow: Auth → Vendors/Slots → Bookings (pending) → Payments (confirm). Import into Postman; the Session request auto-saves {{token}}. See docs/booking-flow.md.\n\n## Stripe Connect note\nCard `create-intent` is blocked until the vendor has `payoutsEnabled`. Vendor must complete `POST /api/vendor/payouts/onboard` first (see Pawffy API — Unified / Vendor collection).\nProduction: https://pawffy-backend-yyed.onrender.com\n\n\n## Reviews\nFolder **⭐ Reviews (Customer ↔ Vendor)**: customer rates vendor + vendor rates customer after completed booking. Set `vendorId` (business UUID) and `bookingId`. Switch `token` between customer and partner JWTs as noted in each step.\n",
    "_postman_id": "pawffy-unified-booking-collection",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "supabaseAccessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "vendorId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "serviceId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "petId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "bookingId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "paymentIntentId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "couponCode",
      "value": "SAVE10",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "productionBaseUrl",
      "value": "https://pawffy-backend-yyed.onrender.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "localBaseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5001",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "businessId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "businessReviewId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "customerReviewId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Session (exchange Supabase token)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data && r.data.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', r.data.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', r.data.user.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"accessToken\": \"{{supabaseAccessToken}}\",\n  \"name\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "session"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Exchange a Supabase accessToken for the app JWT. Token is auto-saved to {{token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "auth",
                "me"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🐾 Pets",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Pet",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data && r.data.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('petId', r.data.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Buddy\",\n  \"species\": \"dog\",\n  \"breed\": \"Golden Retriever\",\n  \"gender\": \"male\",\n  \"age\": 3\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/pets",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "pets"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Creates a pet and auto-saves {{petId}} for booking."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Pets",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/pets",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "pets"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🏪 Vendors (Discovery)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Vendors",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendors?serviceType=groomer&city=&isOnline=true",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendors"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "serviceType",
                  "value": "groomer",
                  "description": "Optional: vet|groomer|walker|trainer|sitter|boarding|transport|poop_scooper"
                },
                {
                  "key": "city",
                  "value": "",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "latitude",
                  "value": "",
                  "description": "Optional; must be paired with longitude",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "longitude",
                  "value": "",
                  "disabled": true
                },
                {
                  "key": "isOnline",
                  "value": "true",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Public. Browse verified providers. Copy an id into {{vendorId}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Vendor By ID (+ services)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data && r.data.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('vendorId', r.data.id); }",
                  "if (r.data && Array.isArray(r.data.services) && r.data.services[0]) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('serviceId', r.data.services[0].id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendors",
                "{{vendorId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Public. Provider profile + active services. Auto-saves {{vendorId}} and the first {{serviceId}} when present."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Vendor Slots",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}/slots?date=2026-12-25&serviceId={{serviceId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendors",
                "{{vendorId}}",
                "slots"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "date",
                  "value": "2026-12-25",
                  "description": "Required. YYYY-MM-DD"
                },
                {
                  "key": "serviceId",
                  "value": "{{serviceId}}",
                  "description": "Optional. Uses the service duration for the slot grid"
                },
                {
                  "key": "slotDurationMinutes",
                  "value": "30",
                  "description": "Optional 10-240 (ignored when serviceId given)",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Public. Available time slots for the given date."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📅 Bookings",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Booking (status=pending)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data && r.data.id) { pm.collectionVariables.set('bookingId', r.data.id); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"vendorId\": \"{{vendorId}}\",\n  \"serviceId\": \"{{serviceId}}\",\n  \"petId\": \"{{petId}}\",\n  \"bookingDate\": \"2026-12-25\",\n  \"bookingTime\": \"14:30\",\n  \"location\": \"123 Main St, New York\",\n  \"notes\": \"Pet needs a bath and nail trim\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "bookings"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Customer only. Creates a PartnerBooking with status=pending. bookingTime accepts HH:MM or HH:MM AM/PM. Auto-saves {{bookingId}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get My Bookings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings?status=pending",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "bookings"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "pending",
                  "description": "Optional: pending|confirmed|completed|cancelled|rejected",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Booking By ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "bookings",
                "{{bookingId}}"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Owner only. Includes business, service, payment, appointmentId, dateTimeFormatted."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Cancel Booking",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"cancelled\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/bookings/{{bookingId}}/status",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "bookings",
                "{{bookingId}}",
                "status"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Customer (owner) only. Only 'cancelled' is accepted; works when the booking is pending or confirmed."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "⭐ Reviews (Customer ↔ Vendor)",
      "description": "Two-way reviews after a **completed** booking.\n\n**Variables needed:** `token` (switch customer/partner JWT), `bookingId`, `vendorId` (same as businessId).\n\n### Run order\n1. Complete a booking end-to-end (pay + vendor complete)\n2. Set `token` = **customer** JWT → **STEP 1** Review Vendor\n3. **STEP 2** Public list (no auth needed)\n4. Set `token` = **partner** JWT → **STEP 3** Vendor inbox + **STEP 4** Reply\n5. Still partner JWT → **STEP 5** Review Customer + **STEP 6** List written\n6. Set `token` = **customer** JWT → **STEP 7** Reviews about me\n\nRules: booking `completed`; one review per booking per direction; rating 1–5.\nProduction: `https://pawffy-backend-yyed.onrender.com`",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "STEP 1 — Customer → Review Vendor",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Use **customer** JWT in `token`. Body needs completed `bookingId`. Also sets `businessId` if you use that var — set `vendorId` = business UUID.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}/reviews",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendors",
                "{{vendorId}}",
                "reviews"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"bookingId\": \"{{bookingId}}\",\n  \"rating\": 5,\n  \"comment\": \"Great service, highly recommend!\"\n}"
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('businessReviewId', r.data.id);",
                  "pm.test('created or already reviewed', () => pm.expect([201,409]).to.include(pm.response.code));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "STEP 2 — Public List Vendor Reviews",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Public. No auth required.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendors/{{vendorId}}/reviews?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendors",
                "{{vendorId}}",
                "reviews"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "STEP 3 — Vendor Inbox (Reviews About Me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Use **partner** JWT.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendor/reviews?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendor",
                "reviews"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "STEP 4 — Vendor Reply to Review",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Use **partner** JWT. `businessReviewId` auto-saved from STEP 1.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendor/reviews/{{businessReviewId}}/reply",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendor",
                "reviews",
                "{{businessReviewId}}",
                "reply"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"replyContent\": \"Thank you for your kind words!\"\n}"
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "STEP 5 — Vendor → Review Customer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "description": "Use **partner** JWT. Same completed `bookingId`.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendor/customer-reviews",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendor",
                "customer-reviews"
              ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"bookingId\": \"{{bookingId}}\",\n  \"rating\": 5,\n  \"comment\": \"Friendly customer, pets were well behaved.\"\n}"
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data?.id) pm.collectionVariables.set('customerReviewId', r.data.id);",
                  "pm.test('created or already reviewed', () => pm.expect([201,409]).to.include(pm.response.code));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "STEP 6 — Vendor List Customer Reviews I Wrote",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Use **partner** JWT.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/vendor/customer-reviews?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "vendor",
                "customer-reviews"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "STEP 7 — Customer Reviews About Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "description": "Use **customer** JWT.",
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/reviews?page=1&limit=20",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "users",
                "me",
                "reviews"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "page",
                  "value": "1"
                },
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            },
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "💳 Payments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Config",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/config",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "config"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Stripe publishable key, currency, supported payment methods."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Price Summary",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/summary/{{bookingId}}?coupon={{couponCode}}",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "summary",
                "{{bookingId}}"
              ],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "coupon",
                  "value": "{{couponCode}}",
                  "description": "Optional coupon code",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Apply Coupon",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"bookingId\": \"{{bookingId}}\",\n  \"code\": \"{{couponCode}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/apply-coupon",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "apply-coupon"
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Payment Intent (Stripe)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const r = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (r.data && r.data.paymentIntentId) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('paymentIntentId', r.data.paymentIntentId);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"bookingId\": \"{{bookingId}}\",\n  \"paymentMethod\": \"card\",\n  \"couponCode\": \"{{couponCode}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/create-intent",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "create-intent"
              ]
            },
            "description": "paymentMethod: card | net_banking. Returns clientSecret for client-side confirmation. Auto-saves {{paymentIntentId}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Confirm Wallet Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"bookingId\": \"{{bookingId}}\",\n  \"couponCode\": \"{{couponCode}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/confirm",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "confirm"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Requires WALLET_PAYMENTS_ENABLED=true. Debits wallet, marks payment paid, sets booking confirmed."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Stripe Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"paymentIntentId\": \"{{paymentIntentId}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/payments/verify",
              "host": [
                "{{baseUrl}}"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "payments",
                "verify"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Confirms payment status with Stripe and moves the booking pending → confirmed on success."
          }
        },
        {
